node.text:
Sharing my thoughts after trying out the XP-Pen's Innovator 16 for 3 months!! Overall I'm so glad that this was my first graphic display tablet because it made me understand why people invest in them instead of cheaper tablets, with its highly responsive screen, low power consumption, and smart and sleek design. 

Those of you who have been following my IG stories would know that I've been suffering from art block for months, which frankly made me worried if I could draw for this review....but you'll be able to see from the Draw With Me part of the video how its ergonomic design really helped me maintain my focus to break through the horrid block like it was nothing???!

If this got you interested in the Innovator 16 too, here's your chance because XP-Pen wants to share the joy with one of you with a 🔊 GIVEAWAY 🔊!! (Go visit the giveaway post for instructions to participate!) 

Also if you're looking to purchase the Innovator 16, it is currently 20% off with Mother's Day sales until 18 May!!!! Act fast and save more than 100USD!

US store: https://bit.ly/3vyOzCy
CA store: https://bit.ly/3tgj1A2
(Also linked in my bio for your convenience)

#sponsoredpost #innovator16 #xppen

If your interest has been perked about the Innovator 16 too, here's your chance because XP-Pen wants to share the joy with one of you with a 🔊GIVEAWAY 🔊!!

Follow these simple steps to win a FREE Innovator 16:

🌟 Follow @kkumri @xppen_usa and @xppen_ca
📱 Share the giveaway post *publicly* on your IG story and tag @kkumri @xppen_usa and @xppen_ca
💬 Leave a comment on the giveaway post sharing with us WHY you want the Innovator 16 or a graphic display tablet in general (You can watch my review and share about what intrigued you the most!)

Giveaway will take place from 13 May to 27 May (ends 1030AM PT) and I will be announcing the winner the day after, on the 28th! 

Winner will have to reply within 24 hours or a new one will be chosen.

Best of luck and thankyou XP-Pen for making this possible!🍀🍀🍀
